# Projects
* Foodpoints+
An app for Duke Students to track their food spending. Built with Node.js, MongoDB, Angular.js. Has reached 250 monthly active users.

* Memento -  Use Bluetooth Beacons to allow people to securely store photos at locations. Built on Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB. 1 of 10 Final Round Projects for Hackathon@SG.
